                                    <condition>Leaves missing after <locusGrp>
                                            <locus from="1" to="1" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="491" to="491" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="494" to="494" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="502" to="502" scheme="folios"/>
                                        </locusGrp>. <locus from="2" to="2" scheme="folios"/>: bottom part of leaf torn out. <locus from="2" to="11" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="491" to="491" scheme="folios"/>: slash in the inner margin, perhaps from leaves that were excised before and after these leaves. Leaves dirty and stained in places, dirt or some sort of loose particles stuck in the gutter in places, e.g between <locus from="15" to="15" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="16" to="16" scheme="folios"/>. <locus from="226" to="227" scheme="folios"/>: outer part of leaves damaged resulting in loss of a a few letters from the text.</condition>
